  "texts": [
    "Online instruments for generating texts, images, sounds, videos, etc., based on AI technology have become available to a large number of people.",
    "At the end of 2022, OpenAI released ChatGPT, and people started to test this text-generating system, initially perceiving chatbot as a playful activity.",
    "Nevertheless, users discovered the generative potential of the language model and began to use it for more advanced tasks, such as writing books.",
    "In Ukraine, two publishing houses used AI technology in their products (Kryzhnia, 2023; Boiko, 2023) to draw attention to the AI-using ethical issues.",
    "In the USA, the situation appears to be more expository, i.e., the Amazon site removed suspicious AIgenerated books that imitated the work of real authors and limited the number of possible books published to three per day."
